<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>my homepage</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@400;600&family=Quicksand&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
  background: #f7d6e6;
  color: #5a2a3a;
}

/* header */
.header {
  background: #f6f0dc;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}

.header h1 {
  font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  margin: 0;
}

.header p {
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* grid layout */
.section {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
}

/* blocks */
.block {
  padding: 30px;
}

.red {
  background: #e63946;
  color: white;
}

.cream {
  background: #f6f0dc;
}

.pink {
  background: #ffd6e7;
}

.block h2 {
  font-family: 'Fredoka', sans-serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
}

.block img {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/* full width section */
.full {
  padding: 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* fun sticker text */
.sticker {
  background: #ff8fab;
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 8px 15px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

/* mobile */
@media(max-width: 800px) {
  .section {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="header">
  <h1>daniela's world</h1>
  <p>a collection of things i love</p>
</div>

<!-- ME + BIOLOGY -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="block cream">
    <h2>me</h2>
    <p>
      i wanted this page to feel like me instead of a formal introduction.
      something soft, pink, and a little chaotic.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_6481.jpg">
  </div>

  <div class="block red">
    <h2>biology</h2>
    <p>
      biology makes everything feel deeper.
      like there’s always something hidden underneath what we see.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_6651.jpeg">
  </div>
</div>

<!-- BUTTERFLY + DRINKS -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="block pink">
    <h2>butterflies</h2>
    <p>
      my favorite mix of art and science.
      delicate but still alive.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_7529.jpeg">
  </div>

  <div class="block cream">
    <h2>little moments</h2>
    <p>
      i like keeping memories that feel simple but meaningful.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_9172.jpeg">
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CATS -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="block red">
    <h2>my cats</h2>
    <p>
      they make everything feel calmer and softer.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_7303.jpeg">
  </div>

  <div class="block pink">
    <h2>christmas birthday</h2>
    <p>
      my birthday being on christmas makes everything feel warmer.
    </p>
    <img src="IMG_7379 (1).JPG">
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="full cream">
  <p>
    this isn’t just a homepage, it’s a collection of things i love ♡
  </p>
  <div class="sticker">made with pink + memories</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
